song.title: Vote4me
song.info:
Ranked 6th in the 4 channel music compo at Assembly 1994.
Lyrics:
Yo, yo! Let's go!
This is Leinad of Avalanche fame I'm out of money and know what to blame But I got an idea.. why don't you vote4me? In the music competition and then we'll see
I will be so happy with the tiny little prize Of course, I will mind some cash But if you vote4me and I'll be among the free Chances off that you will leave to see tomorrow(?)
-repeat- Vote4me! I wanna win the competition (yeah) Vote4me! I wanna have sum bitchin' (uhuh) Vote4me! I wanna win the competition Vote4me! (uhuh-uhuh) -repeat-
